grab the cup on the counter
turn right, walk to the microwave
open the microwave, put the cup in, heat the cup, take the cup out
turn around, turn around to the cabinet
open the second to the right cabinet door, put the cup in

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the black mug off of the counter to the left of the sink.
Turn right and walk over to the microwave.
Microwave the mug for a couple seconds in the microwave then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn around and look down.
Open the second lower cabinet door from the right and put the heated mug inside, then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated mug in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go forward to the stove, turn right and go to the sink.
Pick up the coffee mug that is on the left side of the sink.
Turn right, go forward to the microwave that is on the left.
Put the coffee mug inside the microwave, turn it on to heat up, take the mug out when it is done.
Turn around, move to the left, turn around and back up.
Put the coffee mug inside the second cabinet from the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a hot coffee mug inside a cabinet.
